Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.40,0:00:02.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zanpakuto…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.40,0:00:07.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Their shape and abilities are\Nbased on their Soul Reaper's soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.60,0:00:10.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Soul Reapers gain power
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.00,0:00:15.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,by learning their names\Nand synergizing with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.93,0:00:21.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They are born with Soul Reapers\Nand die with Soul Reapers.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.83,0:00:24.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is what Zanpakuto are.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.53,0:02:00.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A man named Muramasa\Ncauses all of the Zanpakuto
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.30,0:02:03.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to take physical form and attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.04,0:02:08.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unable to use their Shikai,\Nthe Soul Reapers are overpowered.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.44,0:02:10.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Zanpakuto deliver\Na serious blow to
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.74,0:02:12.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the Thirteen Court Guard Squads\Nin a single night and leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.74,0:02:17.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Seireitei is now in\Na confused, critical state.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.05,0:02:21.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Meanwhile, Rukia walks\Nthrough the Seireitei alone
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.49,0:02:24.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,in search of Byakuya,\Nwho has gone missing,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.96,0:02:28.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,when Sodenoshirayuki\Nappears before her once again.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.07,0:02:36.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sodenoshirayuki…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.90,0:02:39.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You will now be free.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.58,0:02:45.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rukia!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.58,0:02:50.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was some show.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.12,0:02:56.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who the hell are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.12,0:02:59.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am a…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.53,0:03:02.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zanpakuto.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.57,0:03:18.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey there, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.38,0:03:22.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you see anything interesting?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.31,0:03:25.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's none of your business.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.87,0:03:27.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with the attitude?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.52,0:03:28.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's really unpleasant.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.02,0:03:33.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you ignoring us?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.29,0:03:34.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't bother.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.63,0:03:37.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no point in fighting.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.90,0:03:40.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our enemies are over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.33,0:03:42.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.23,0:03:45.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They won't get away next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.00,0:03:48.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to get back\Nat that annoying bastard.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.31,0:03:50.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You’re right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.08,0:03:57.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This time, I get to kill the guy\Nwho calls me by a weird name.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.65,0:04:02.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Let's teach them a lesson.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.83,0:04:14.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a Zanpakuto?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.88,0:04:16.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.07,0:04:20.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sodenoshirayuki…\Nleave this to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.52,0:04:21.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You retreat for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.12,0:04:23.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.28,0:04:26.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.51,0:04:29.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you going,\NIchigo Kurosaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.65,0:04:32.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How do you know my name?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.82,0:04:34.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is not important.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.19,0:04:37.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! What are you up to?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.39,0:04:43.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My goal is to release the Zanpakuto\Nfrom the Soul Reapers.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.48,0:04:45.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.40,0:04:47.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I get it…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.20,0:04:50.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one behind all this!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.30,0:04:56.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, tell me how Rukia\Ncan get her Zanpakuto back!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.54,0:05:01.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo Kurosaki,\Nwhat is a Zanpakuto?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.71,0:05:02.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.01,0:05:08.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zanpakuto are souls that are born\Nwithin the hearts of Soul Reapers.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.45,0:05:12.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They share the same power\Nas their Soul Reaper
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.62,0:05:15.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and exist alongside\Ntheir Soul Reaper's soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.72,0:05:19.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Soul Reapers find the power of
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.03,0:05:22.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the Zanpakuto hidden\Nwithin their souls.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.87,0:05:25.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They converse with their Zanpakuto,\Ncome to an understanding
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.34,0:05:28.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and are able to draw from\Ntheir power by learning their name.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.27,0:05:36.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A few chosen Soul Reapers can\Ngain even more powerful Bankai,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.48,0:05:41.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,by manifesting an incarnation of\Ntheir Zanpakuto and controlling it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.85,0:05:45.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You and the captains\Nhave done this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.49,0:05:50.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But living alongside\NSoul Reapers
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.29,0:05:53.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is not the only way\Nfor a Zanpakuto to live.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.53,0:05:54.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.63,0:05:59.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m saying that a Zanpakuto\Nhas its own will.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.27,0:06:01.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A Zanpakuto’s will?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.24,0:06:06.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Zanpakuto are not\Na part of a Soul Reaper.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.61,0:06:08.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We are separate souls.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.28,0:06:12.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our existence is equal\Nto that of Soul Reapers.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.92,0:06:16.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you find that unbelievable?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.49,0:06:20.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is proof of how arrogant\Nyou Soul Reapers are.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.84,0:06:22.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.09,0:06:24.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the reason why I exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.50,0:06:28.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can understand\Nthe Zanpakuto’s will.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.70,0:06:30.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can talk to their souls.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.30,0:06:36.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I can give physical forms to\Nthose who share the same goals.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.31,0:06:38.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.08,0:06:42.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zanpakuto who answer\Nmy call become
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.28,0:06:46.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,separated from their Soul Reapers\Nand appear in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.87,0:06:50.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is the power given to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.36,0:06:53.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why would the Zanpakuto\Nrespond to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.16,0:06:59.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is the will of Zanpakuto\Nwho have been oppressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.80,0:07:01.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.70,0:07:10.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have never thought of\NSodenoshirayuki as an inferior.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.51,0:07:13.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rukia!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.15,0:07:16.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is just your\Nown one-sided opinion.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.25,0:07:21.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As you can see, Sodenoshirayuki\Nhas responded to my call.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.05,0:07:23.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop pushing yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.79,0:07:26.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your have served your purpose.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.93,0:07:29.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.93,0:07:31.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you really think\Nthat you were able to
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.83,0:07:34.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,escape to the World of\Nthe Living on your own?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.80,0:07:35.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.10,0:07:40.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to release all Zanpakuto\Nfrom their Soul Reapers.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.60,0:07:42.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No exceptions.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.61,0:07:48.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In order to do that, I needed you,\NIchigo Kurosaki, to come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.16,0:07:51.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You let Rukia go on purpose?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.58,0:07:56.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome to my world.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.80,0:07:59.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.89,0:08:03.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right. You rest here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.53,0:08:06.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let you get away with this!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.10,0:08:08.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's move away from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.63,0:08:09.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do whatever you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.57,0:08:14.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.43,0:08:42.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Getsugatensho!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.31,0:08:56.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is he?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.89,0:09:09.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Put away your sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.79,0:09:12.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.09,0:09:37.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's useless.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.53,0:09:49.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.48,0:09:59.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.81,0:10:00.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell did you do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.32,0:10:10.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.33,0:10:18.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hear my voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.43,0:10:25.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Follow your instincts\Nand release your soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.91,0:10:40.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Discard your fear. Look ahead.\NGo forth. Don't stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.55,0:10:47.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you turn back, you'll grow old.\NIf you're hesitant, you'll die.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.63,0:10:56.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come. Your name is…Zangetsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.81,0:11:10.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.19,0:11:11.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.96,0:11:22.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zangetsu… Why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.10,0:11:32.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Old Man Zangetsu!\NWhat's the meaning of this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.27,0:11:35.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Answer me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.37,0:11:39.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Weren't we of\None mind and body?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.58,0:11:43.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.51,0:12:12.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can still move?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.34,0:12:14.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's over now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.49,0:12:26.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Old Man…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.19,0:12:30.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.73,0:12:32.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.46,0:12:36.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Getsugatensho.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.31,0:12:55.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Unohana!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.74,0:12:57.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Isane?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.76,0:13:00.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ma'am! I have a report\Nfrom Squad Twelve.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.15,0:13:06.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zanpakuto have become\Nseparate entities?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.03,0:13:06.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.92,0:13:08.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What does that mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.69,0:13:12.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the conclusion that\NMaster Mayuri has come to
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.72,0:13:16.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,after testing this phenomenon\Non his own body.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.66,0:13:18.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could you give us the details?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.88,0:13:19.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.40,0:13:33.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It seems the Zanpakuto's soul\Nreally has left my body.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.63,0:13:39.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Interesting. Truly interesting.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.62,0:13:43.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Master Mayuri, aren't Zanpakuto\Nand Soul Reapers{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.02,0:13:47.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}different manifestations\Nof the same soul?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.08,0:13:49.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Normally, that is the case.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.96,0:13:53.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But now they have become\Nentirely separate entities.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.38,0:13:55.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Is such a thing possible...?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.25,0:13:57.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's why this is interesting.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.30,0:14:00.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You're so worthless.\NDon't act as if you understand!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.63,0:14:07.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But how was this made possible?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.93,0:14:14.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The situation is much worse\Nthan I had imagined.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.62,0:14:18.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm… May I ask a question?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.21,0:14:21.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since they're separate entities,\Nwhat'll happen if we defeat
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.22,0:14:24.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,one of the Zanpakuto\Nmanifestations in battle?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.79,0:14:25.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.43,0:14:30.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Would we lose our\NZanpakuto forever?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.97,0:14:32.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.51,0:14:34.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I cannot say\Nfor certain because
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.74,0:14:36.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we don't have enough data.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.22,0:14:37.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.74,0:14:38.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.44,0:14:43.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's leave this to\NCaptain Kurotsuchi.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.48,0:14:45.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm… One more thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.95,0:14:48.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Master Mayuri has a request\Nfor you, Captain Unohana.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.42,0:14:49.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.60,0:14:54.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He wants you to provide him with\Ndata on the Soul Reapers who are
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.10,0:14:57.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,receiving treatment from Squad Four\Nso that he can analyze it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.05,0:15:01.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Certainly. I will have it\Nall sent to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.19,0:15:01.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Also…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.61,0:15:06.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He wants to gather data\Non you, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.47,0:15:10.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Does he want Captain Unohana\Nto go all the way to
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.14,0:15:11.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the Department of Research\Nand Development?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.25,0:15:17.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. He said he needed\Ndata on captains.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.35,0:15:18.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.68,0:15:19.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.82,0:15:21.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right, Isane.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.87,0:15:24.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But… Umm…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.69,0:15:29.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But for Captain Kurotsuchi to\Nbe personally inspecting your body
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.07,0:15:32.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is so invasive.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.51,0:15:35.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're in a race\Nagainst time, Isane.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.01,0:15:38.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.43,0:15:43.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In return, I want you to report\Nto us any new findings.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.95,0:15:45.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.36,0:15:46.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.42,0:15:48.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Reporting!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.88,0:15:52.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Large-scale combat has been\Nconfirmed in the Seireitei!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.39,0:15:55.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Spiritual Pressures\Nat the scene belong to
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.62,0:15:57.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rukia Kuchiki of\NSquad Thirteen
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.89,0:16:00.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and Substitute Soul Reaper\NIchigo Kurosaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.28,0:16:22.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.31,0:16:47.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who the hell are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.57,0:16:52.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you Ichigo Kurosaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.58,0:16:58.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the other soul\Nthat lives within him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.59,0:17:00.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Other soul?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.20,0:17:02.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Getsuga…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.68,0:17:04.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,…tensho!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.40,0:17:29.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Instant regeneration…?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.71,0:18:36.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This Spiritual Pressure…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.67,0:19:40.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As I suspected...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.30,0:20:04.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.01,0:20:09.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I won't give it to you…\NI won't give it to you…{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.29,0:20:12.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm not giving this body to you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.00,0:20:18.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Don't do things\Nwithout my permission!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.85,0:21:22.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zangetsu…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.37,0:21:34.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zan…ge…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.92,0:21:47.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This man…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.11,0:23:22.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why, Old Man Zangetsu?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.11,0:23:24.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm bored with your internal world.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.95,0:23:28.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all buildings.\NThere's no greenery.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.18,0:23:30.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to see forests.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.36,0:23:32.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to see\Nthe grandeur of nature.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.95,0:23:34.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make a garden for you…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.89,0:23:39.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.90,0:23:41.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How come the Women’s\NSoul Reaper Association
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.54,0:23:43.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,gets to go to the beach?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.12,0:23:45.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We should also take\Na vacation at the beach!!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.01,0:23:47.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to have\Na summer adventure!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.60,0:23:49.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right! Me too…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.11,0:23:51.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.34,0:23:54.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s settled!\NWe're going to the beach too!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.18,0:23:56.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the paperwork is tedious.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.02,0:23:58.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do something about that!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.14,0:23:59.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do it, Chairman!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.32,0:24:00.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,– All right!\N	– All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.32,0:24:01.28,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,THEIR HARD WORK PAID OFF.\NNOW, OFF TO THE BEACH!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.53,0:24:03.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did we do to deserve this?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.78,0:24:05.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,